(3334, 'Sara', 'editor_sara@dopress.com', 'http://www.dopress.com', 'Dear Sir or Madam,\r\n\r\nI am Sara, an editor of Dopress Books who focuses on creating high quality books on graphic design, interior design and architecture. I found some exciting works on your website. I like your design style, it is my pleasure to invite you to submit your relevant works for our books titled:\r\n \r\n1. Identity by Color - cutting-edge designs about brand/identity system from the talented design teams worldwide\r\n     190 x 260 mm, 352 pages, English\r\n\r\n2. Play Fonts - cutting-edge designs inspired by the font application\r\n     190 x 260 mm, 352 pages, English\r\n\r\n3. No One Missing - 1000 cutting-edge designs inspired by illustrations\r\n     190 x 260 mm, 352 pages, English\r\n\r\n4. Wall Art - cutting-edge wall designs including wall painting, wallpaper and wall decorations, etc.\r\n     190 x 260 mm, 352 pages, English\r\n\r\n\r\nYou need not to pay any money for the publications, and you only need to provide some materials such as photo images, credits, texts, and profile with contact details. We think that it is a good opportunity to show your design style and your business in all over the world. \r\n\r\nPlease feel free to contact me for more information if you have some interests in publishing your works. \r\n\r\nLook forward to your reply.\r\n\r\nKindest Regards,\r\n\r\nSara\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nDopress Books \r\ngraphic. interior. architecture\r\n\r\nAdd: 407, No.85-3, Huanghe South Street, \r\n110031 Shenyang, China\r\nTel: +86-24-88622666; Fax: +86-24-88680777\r\nWeb: http://www.dopress.com\r\nEmail: editor_sara@dopress.com\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n', 4, '1274156514'),
